reviewText: Luv Alton, love the science & wish he would come back.  First rate product & quick in mail.

I think I'll continue looking for the show season by season, though. Subject matter is good, but there wasn't a show where I didn't learn something, so I want all of them and keeping up with them episode by episode is a pain. Seasons are the thing for me.
as new quality dvds. slight wear on cases but was mentioned in description. recommended for those who love good eats and are on budget.
